{"to":["alex@erc.org"],"subject":"Visitor Data Summary – January 2022","body":"Hi Alex,

As requested, here is a high-level summary of our visitor activity for January 2022:

• Total unique visitors (approx.): 120
• Breakdown by visitor type (percentage of total):
  – Corporate partners / clients: ~45%
  – Vendors & service providers: ~30%
  – Prospective employees / interviewees: ~15%
  – General guests & facility tours: ~10%

Primary reasons for visits:
• Business meetings and project check-ins
• Scheduled deliveries and equipment servicing
• Recruitment interviews
• Guided tours for prospective partners and community guests

Traffic patterns:
• Visitor volume clustered around mid-week afternoons, with no notable security or compliance issues reported.

Please let me know if you need any further analysis or if you would like to access the full internal log (contains personally identifiable information and is stored securely in Notion).

Best regards,
[Your Name]"}
